{"tid":2316698,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"嶺南大學譴責陳雲肆意侮辱他人","createTime":"2020-12-08T05:10:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-08T05:14:48.000Z","uid":5195,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"eeae0b993f315fc13d3fccc9d0c1c784a374ce60","tid":2316698,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T05:10:17.000Z","msg":"人稱「國師」的陳雲日前在社交平台出帖，形容衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君醫生的丈夫因癌症病逝是「好消息」，引發爭議，他又指如何網民有何不滿，可以去信嶺南大學投訴解僱他。<br />\n<br />\n嶺南大學（8日）指留意到陳雲在社交媒體上涉及侮辱衞生防護中心官員，並呼籲他人到嶺大投訴。嶺南大學嚴正聲明，嶺大早於2016年8月已經終止陳雲的教職，此後陳先生與嶺大並無任何關係。聲明又指陳雲肆意侮辱他人，行為涼薄冷血，令人不齒，嶺大嚴正讉責，並保留追究他試圖誤導公眾、影響嶺大聲譽的權利。"},{"pid":"59258485baeb6ca43206ee8a53611ebc05428e2e","tid":2316698,"uid":334957,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T05:12:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de9ab12818558f5a8d00ac9eeece0884d7e6540a","tid":2316698,"uid":58387,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T05:14:10.000Z","msg":"嶺大<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad63cd5a46b9c85fe8e514f911f9f2cfecd9d243","tid":2316698,"uid":128705,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T05:14:30.000Z","msg":"告就告 唔告就唔告<br />\n咩保留追究權利<br />\n根本就吹陳雲唔漲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9bd7334902bcbd85d7f65adf282352901ecc662","tid":2316698,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T05:14:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 